graph LR
    Notebooks["Notebooks<br/>(Workbench Images)"]

    %% External Dependencies (Build-Time Base Layers)
    Notebooks -->|base layer<br/>CPU| AIPCC_CPU["AIPCC Base (CPU)<br/>UBI9 + Python 3.12"]
    Notebooks -->|base layer<br/>CUDA| AIPCC_CUDA["AIPCC Base (CUDA)<br/>NVIDIA CUDA toolkit"]
    Notebooks -->|base layer<br/>ROCm| AIPCC_ROCm["AIPCC Base (ROCm)<br/>AMD ROCm toolkit"]

    %% External Dependencies (Build-Time Tools)
    Notebooks -->|build stage| UBI9_Python["ubi9/python-312<br/>Wheel caching"]
    Notebooks -->|build stage<br/>mongocli FIPS| UBI9_Go["ubi9/go-toolset<br/>Go compiler"]
    Notebooks -->|repo config| UBI9["ubi9/ubi<br/>ubi.repo source"]

    %% Bundled IDE/Runtime Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|IDE: jupyter-*| JupyterLab["JupyterLab 4.4"]
    Notebooks -->|IDE: codeserver| CodeServerDep["code-server v4.104.0"]
    Notebooks -->|IDE: rstudio-*| RStudioDep["RStudio Server<br/>2025.09"]
    Notebooks -->|proxy| NGINX["NGINX 1.24"]
    Notebooks -->|runtime| NodeJS["Node.js 22.18.0"]
    Notebooks -->|runtime: rstudio| R["R 4.5.1"]
    Notebooks -->|runtime: trustyai| Java17["Java 17 (OpenJDK)"]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tool| OC["OpenShift CLI (oc)"]
    Notebooks -->|DB tool| MongoCLI["mongocli 2.0.4"]

    %% Internal Platform Dependencies
    NotebookCtrl["odh-notebook-controller"] -->|launches pods<br/>injects sidecar| Notebooks
    Operator["rhods-operator"] -->|deploys<br/>ImageStreams| Notebooks
    Dashboard["RHOAI Dashboard"] -->|image selection<br/>UI| Notebooks
    KubeRBAC["kube-rbac-proxy"] -->|sidecar<br/>:8443 HTTPS| Notebooks
    KFP["Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>/ Tekton"] -->|runs runtime<br/>images| Notebooks
    Elyra["Elyra"] -.->|bundled in<br/>datascience images| Notebooks
    CodeflareSDK["Codeflare-SDK"] -.->|bundled library| Notebooks
    KubeflowTraining["Kubeflow Training"] -.->|bundled library| Notebooks

    %% External Runtime Services
    Notebooks -->|pipeline artifacts| S3["S3-compatible Storage"]
    Notebooks -->|API calls| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP"]
    Notebooks -->|image pull| Registry["registry.redhat.io<br/>/ Quay.io"]

    %% Build System
    Konflux["Konflux CI/CD"] -->|builds from<br/>Dockerfile.konflux.*| Notebooks

